text: Jaroslav Bím (12 January 1931 - 2012) was a Czech gymnast. He competed at the 1956 Summer Olympics and the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1931 births Category:2012 deaths Category:Czech male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Czechoslovakia Category:Gymnasts at the 1956 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:People from Kyjov
